flowchart TD
    A[LLM Planner Output] --> B[Queue Ingestion + Idempotency Check]

    B --> C{Mutability?}

    C -->|readonly| D[queued - readonly]
    C -->|mutating| E[queued - mutating]

    D --> F[ready]

    E --> G[Preflight - laeuft immer auch im autoconfirmmode]
    G --> PR{Preflight invalid + retry hint?}
    PR -->|yes + runtime retry gate passes| OB
    PR -->|yes + gate fails| U[clarification returned via ai_send_message]
    PR -->|no| H{Hard block?}
    H -->|validation_error / permission_error| O[failed - terminal]
    H -->|domain_conflict| DC[blocked_confirmation - domain]
    DC --> J[User Confirm or Clarification]
    H -->|autoconfirmmode active| F
    H -->|normal mode| I[blocked_confirmation - awaiting confirm]
    I --> J
    J --> F

    F --> SL{Scheduler-Lock - max 1 running per thread_id}
    SL -->|slot free| K[running]
    SL -->|slot occupied| F

    K --> L{Execution Result}

    L -->|success| M[succeeded]
    L -->|transient error - provider_timeout / io| N[retry_waiting]
    N --> F
    L -->|contract_repair - CONTRACT issue_codes| RP[Neuer Queue-Eintrag mit depends_on]
    RP --> B
    L -->|domain error - recoverable| P[failed - execution failure + Observation with error detail]

    M --> OB[Observation Builder]
    P --> OB
    O --> OB
    U --> OB

    OB --> RR{Repair needed?}
    RR -->|yes - LLM emits new command| B
    RR -->|no| LS{MAX_LOOP_STEPS Budget ok?}
    LS -->|exhausted| FAIL[failed - budget exceeded]
    LS -->|ok| GR{Goal reached?}

    GR -->|yes| S[Final Synthesis]
    GR -->|no - observations insufficient| T[Re-Plan: new LLM step - nur anhaengen - simple_retrieval - kein neuer initialer Catalog/Embedding-Start]
    T --> B

    DEPCHECK{depends_on auf failed Item?} -->|yes| SK[skipped - terminal]

    style M fill:#2d6a4f,color:#fff
    style O fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style P fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style U fill:#e9c46a,color:#000
    style SK fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style FAIL fill:#9b2226,color:#fff
    style S fill:#1d3557,color:#fff
    style I fill:#e9c46a,color:#000
    style DC fill:#e9c46a,color:#000
    style RP fill:#457b9d,color:#fff
    style SL fill:#264653,color:#fff
    style LS fill:#264653,color:#fff